              We have emailed a 6-digit confirmation code to acb@domain, please enter the code in below box to verify
              your email.
            </Typography>

            <Box sx={{ mt: 5, mb: 3 }}>
              <VerifyCodeForm />
            </Box>

            <Typography variant="body2" align="center">
